        <p>A pretty useful tool for tracking when a change happens to a site. I use it for sites that don&#39;t update often, or don&#39;t have an RSS feed.</p>
<p>Whenever a site changes by a certain %, you will receive an email with a link to the diff between the two pages.</p>
<h3>ChangeDetection - Know when any web page changes\n</h3>
<p><a href="http://www.changedetection.com">http://www.changedetection.com</a></p>

